---
/**
 * rest-api · 0011 · Figure 1 — "The senior API-design framework" flowchart.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from
 * docs/rest-api/lessons/0011-mock-interview-whiteboard-design.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption). It lives as an .astro component, NOT inline in the
 * MDX, because MDX's JSX parser is unreliable with raw inline SVG that uses
 * kebab-case attributes (text-anchor, font-size, stroke-width, marker-end, …).
 * In an .astro file the SVG is plain HTML, so it renders byte-for-byte. The
 * marker ids (arw, arwA, arwR) reference the shared <defs> block that the lesson
 * body keeps near the top of the page.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 360"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A flowchart of the senior API design framework: clarify requirements, model resources, choose methods and status codes, add pagination and filtering, secure with auth and object-level checks, design errors and rate limits, plan versioning and evolution, then close on edge cases and scale"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="320"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">DIAGNOSE FIRST, THEN DESIGN — RUN THIS SPINE TOP TO BOTTOM</text
            >

            <rect
                x="200"
                y="30"
                width="240"
                height="34"
                rx="9"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="320"
                y="51"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">① CLARIFY requirements &amp; constraints</text
            >

            <rect x="200" y="78" width="240" height="34" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#1f3a5a"></rect>
            <text
                x="320"
                y="99"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">② MODEL resources &amp; URIs</text
            >

            <rect x="200" y="126" width="240" height="34" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#6b675f"
            ></rect>
            <text x="320" y="147" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700"
                >③ METHODS + status codes</text
            >

            <rect x="200" y="174" width="240" height="34" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#6b675f"
            ></rect>
            <text x="320" y="195" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700"
                >④ PAGINATION · filter · sort</text
            >

            <rect x="200" y="222" width="240" height="34" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="320"
                y="243"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">⑤ AUTH + object-level (BOLA)</text
            >

            <rect x="200" y="270" width="240" height="34" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="320"
                y="291"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">⑥ ERRORS + rate limits</text
            >

            <rect x="200" y="318" width="240" height="34" rx="9" fill="#1c1b18" stroke="#1c1b18"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="320"
                y="339"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#f3efe3">⑦ VERSIONING → edge cases → 100×</text
            >

            <line x1="320" y1="64" x2="320" y2="78" stroke="#7a1f12" marker-end="url(#arwA)"></line>
            <line x1="320" y1="112" x2="320" y2="126" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <line x1="320" y1="160" x2="320" y2="174" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <line x1="320" y1="208" x2="320" y2="222" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <line x1="320" y1="256" x2="320" y2="270" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <line x1="320" y1="304" x2="320" y2="318" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>

            <!-- side rail: idempotency hooks into writes -->
            <rect
                x="452"
                y="78"
                width="180"
                height="130"
                rx="9"
                fill="#fbfaf2"
                stroke="#d8d4c8"
                stroke-dasharray="4 3"></rect>
            <text
                x="542"
                y="98"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">ON EVERY WRITE</text
            >
            <text x="542" y="116" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >idempotency key + dedup</text
            >
            <text x="542" y="132" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >caching / If-Match on reads</text
            >
            <text x="542" y="148" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >+ optimistic concurrency</text
            >
            <text
                x="542"
                y="170"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">ON LONG WORK</text
            >
            <text x="542" y="188" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >202 + status resource</text
            >
            <text x="542" y="202" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >signed at-least-once webhooks</text
            >
            <line x1="440" y1="143" x2="452" y2="143" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>

            <!-- left rail: clarify is the gate -->
            <rect
                x="8"
                y="78"
                width="180"
                height="80"
                rx="9"
                fill="#f7ecea"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                stroke-dasharray="4 3"></rect>
            <text
                x="98"
                y="98"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#9a2417">SKIP CLARIFY = FAIL</text
            >
            <text x="98" y="116" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >clients? scale? r/w ratio?</text
            >
            <text x="98" y="131" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >consistency? auth? SLA?</text
            >
            <text x="98" y="148" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#7a2218"
                >pin these before drawing</text
            >
            <line x1="188" y1="47" x2="200" y2="47" stroke="#9a2417" marker-end="url(#arwR)"></line>
            <path
                d="M 98 78 C 98 60, 140 47, 188 47"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                stroke-dasharray="3 2"></path>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Eleven lesson topics collapse into one spine. The writes get idempotency, the reads get
        pagination + caching, long work goes async — all gated by the clarify step.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
